NAME
    Locale::Maketext::Lexicon::Properties - Maketext plugin for
    Data::Properties

SYNOPSIS
      package Foo::L10N;
      use Locale::Maketext::Lexicon {
          en => [ 'Properties', 'properties.en' ],
      };

      package main;
      my $lh = Foo::L10N->get_handle('en');
      print $lh->maketext("email.invalid");

DESCRIPTION
    Locale::Maketext::Lexicon::Properties is a plugin for
    Locale::Maketext::Lexicon which parses "java.util.Properties" file using
    Data::Properties.

AUTHOR
    Tatsuhiko Miyagawa <miyagawa@bulknews.net>

